OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FOil prices have surged back over the
OL,7,F$100 a barrel mark after a series of
OL,8,Fattacks on energy infrastructure
OL,9,Facross the Gulf region, with Iran's
OL,10,Fnew Ayatollah making his first
OL,11,Fstatement since becoming leader.
OL,13,FMojtaba Khamenei declared on Thursday
OL,14,Fthat the Strait of Hormuz should not
OL,15,Fbe reopened, as he vowed that attacks
OL,16,Fon surrounding Gulf countries would
OL,17,Fcontinue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
