OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FAsia has been the hardest hit by
OL,7,Fshortages, with the majority of oil
OL,8,Fand liquefied natural gas passing
OL,9,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz destined
OL,10,Ffor the region.
OL,12,FThe Middle East supplied 60% of Asia's
OL,13,Fcrude oil imports in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
