OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FPakistan's prime minister announced a
OL,7,Fseries of fuel-saving measures on
OL,8,FMonday, including closing schools for
OL,9,Ftwo weeks starting March 16, moving
OL,10,Fgovernment employees to a four-day
OL,11,Fweek, and instructing 50% of
OL,12,Fgovernmental staff to start working
OL,13,Ffrom home.
OL,15,FGovernmental spending is also to be
OL,16,Fcut by 20%, while 60% of official
OL,17,Fvehicles, excluding ambulances and
OL,18,Fbuses, will be taken off the road,
OL,19,FShehbaz Sharif said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
