OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FUniversities in Pakistan and
OL,7,FBangladesh will also close their
OL,8,Fcampuses and move learning online.
OL,10,FBangladesh, which relies on imports
OL,11,Ffor around 95% of its energy, has
OL,12,Fencountered increased power cuts since
OL,13,Fthe war began.
OL,15,FIn the Philippines, government
OL,16,Fofficers are also moving to a four-day
OL,17,Fweek, while officials in Thailand and
OL,18,FVietnam are being encouraged to work
OL,19,Ffrom home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
