OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FLeaders in Thailand and South Korea
OL,7,Fboth confirmed they would set a cap on
OL,8,Ffuel prices, while Sri Lanka's
OL,9,Fgovernment defended a sharp increase
OL,10,Fin cost which it said would work as a
OL,11,Fdeterrent against panic-buying.
OL,13,FIn Vietnam, domestic airlines could
OL,14,Fface fuel shortages from next month if
OL,15,Fthe conflict does not end, the Civil
OL,16,FAviation Authority of Vietnam said.
OL,18,FPetrochemical companies in Singapore
OL,19,Fand Indonesia have declared force
OL,20,Fmajeures over disruption to their
OL,21,Fsupply chains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
