OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FGreece has imposed price controls on
OL,7,Ffuel and household staples, such as
OL,8,Ffood, cleaning supplies and
OL,9,Ftoiletries, with the measures set to
OL,10,Ftake effect until June 30, a
OL,11,Fgovernment spokesman said.
OL,13,FIn the UK, Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,14,Fsaid the government may issue energy
OL,15,Fsupport packages if the cost of fuel
OL,16,Fand energy does not decrease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
