OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FSweden-based airline SAS said it was
OL,7,Ftemporarily increasing its fare prices
OL,8,Fto adjust to the rise in jet fuel
OL,9,Fcosts.
OL,11,FThis week Russian President Vladimir
OL,12,FPutin said his country - the second-
OL,13,Flargest oil exporter in the world -
OL,14,Fwas was willing to work with European
OL,15,Fcustomers again, if they required.
OL,17,FMany European countries have sharply
OL,18,Freduced their reliance on Russian oil
OL,19,Fand gas since 2022, when Putin invaded
OL,20,FUkraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
