OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FAir New Zealand announced on Thursday
OL,7,Fit will be cancelling 1,100 flights
OL,8,Fbetween now and early May due to
OL,9,Fincreases in jet fuel prices.
OL,11,FThe airline is also raising its prices
OL,12,Fon routes still operating, and said it
OL,13,Fmay need to take further action if the
OL,14,Fsituation does not improve.
OL,16,FOfficials in the country have also
OL,17,Fsaid they are considering invoking
OL,18,Femergency powers that could limit how
OL,19,Foften people are allowed to drive
OL,20,Fduring the crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
