OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FWhen last used - following the Iranian
OL,7,Frevolution in 1979 - car owners had to
OL,8,Fnominate one day a week they wouldn't
OL,9,Fdrive and could face a fine if they
OL,10,Fbroke the rules.
OL,12,FAuthorities were also able to restrict
OL,13,Fthe sale of fuel through coupon-usage.
OL,15,FAustralia announced plans to
OL,16,Ftemporarily relax petrol standards to
OL,17,Fallow for a "dirty" fuel, with higher
OL,18,Fsulphur levels, to be mixed in with
OL,19,Fcurrent supply, adding an extra 100
OL,20,Fmillion litres into the system a month
OL,21,Ffor 60 days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
