OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FSulfur is usually removed from petrol
OL,7,Fduring the refining process to reduce
OL,8,Fair pollution.
OL,10,FIn Egypt, the government said it was
OL,11,Flimiting non-essential travel and
OL,12,Frationing street lighting, as fuel
OL,13,Fprices rose by 30% this week.
OL,15,FSpeaking at a press conference, Prime
OL,16,FMinister Moustafa Madbouli said a
OL,17,Fcrisis committee had been formed to
OL,18,Fmonitor the situation, noting that the
OL,19,Fdisruption to supply chains had
OL,20,F"affected many goods and services".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
