OL,3,CFour-day weeks and driving limits: How
OL,4,Cthe world reacts to Iran oil crisis
OL,6,FAnalysts have warned that countries
OL,7,Flike Sudan, The Gambia, Central
OL,8,FAfrican Republic, Lesotho and
OL,9,FZimbabwe, which operate under
OL,10,Fprogrammes from the International
OL,11,FMonetary Fund could struggle as the
OL,12,Fcost of importing energy and fuel
OL,13,Fdrains their limited foreign exchange
OL,14,Freserves.
